        "body": "## Why\n\nClawHub is adding NVIDIA SkillSpector scanning and versioned Skill Cards to the skill trust story. This PR adds the draft OpenClaw blog announcement and the visual assets needed to preview it locally before publishing.\n\n## What Changed\n\n- Added a draft NVIDIA skill security blog post under `src/content/blog`.\n- Added the OpenClaw x NVIDIA title image, Patrick author avatar, SkillSpector screenshot, Skill Card screenshot, and ClawHub scan pipeline image.\n- Allows draft blog posts to render in local dev only, while production builds continue to exclude drafts.\n- Constrains markdown images in blog posts so wide screenshots stay inside the article column.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `bun run build`\n- Local preview at `http://127.0.0.1:4321/blog/openclaw-nvidia-skill-security/`\n- Verified the three body images render within the article column and the Skill Card image uses the updated `skill-card-2.png` source.\n",
